body_html: You have to build the pb file with Version 1.1.0. Or if you check out tf version 1.1.0 from github, there is an iOS example without pod. You could copy that example, edit search paths and then check out latest. Build for iOS and then use your copied example app project. This worked for me. Monday I could give you more informations.
